<span style="font-weight: 400;">The idea that you‚Äôll be a better person without your partner can destroy your motivation to make the relationship work. Keeping in mind that breaking up is a ‚ÄúNO, NO‚Äù can strengthen the bond in your relationship.</span>

<b>Always respect your partner</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Your partner is the best and that‚Äôs why you fell in love with them in the first place. The best way you prove it is by showing them some respect.</span>

<b>Improve your communication</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Nothing can substitute those regular talks and gossips between lovers. When there is sharing of thoughts and feelings, the bond between partners grows stronger. Partners should set aside some time every day to just discuss together.</span>

